Moist snuff: 92 cents/oz. and a proportionate rate on all fractional parts of an ounce;
E-Cigarettes (defined as "vapor products"): 5 cents per fluid milliliter;
All other tobacco products: 30% of the wholesale price.

Wholesalers - each place of business: $200 annually; 
Retailers - each place of business: $50 annually; 
Vending machine operators - each machine: $15 annually.
